58
00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:16.140
So all I'm saying is that you might be making it even harder by refusing to practice your English with non-native speakers.

59
00:04:18.640 --> 00:04:23.800
So the second thing I want you to consider is that everyone knows something you don't.

60
00:04:26.050 --> 00:04:30.810
To think that you can only learn new things about English from native English speakers is the same thinG

