As thinking you can only learn how to play soccer by studying with someone who has been playing since the day they were born.

62
00:04:37.790 --> 00:04:41.810
To think that you can only learn things from a teacher is fine. That's a valid opinion.

63
00:04:42.010 --> 00:04:44.270
But we've got to remember, everyone is a teacher.

64
00:04:45.500 --> 00:04:51.640
